 Render an animation on an element.

```
    div (List.concat
            [ Animation.Pack.render model.style MyStyle
            , [ style
                    [ ( "position", "absolute" )
                    , ( "border-style", "dotted" )
                    ]
               ]
            ]
        )
        [ text "My Animated Div" ]

```
